name: Who Am I? (Sir_Obvious)
description:
"Who Am I?" is a 2D Pixel Platformer with a small narrative about identity.

Made by me (obviously) for the #RainbowJam16 :)

Controls:

Keyboard:

Run: A D
Jump: W
Sprint: A+A || D+D
Teleport: Space

XBox Controller:

Run: Left Analog Stick
Sprint: RB while Running
Jump: A
Teleport: X
